  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这两天，Nano Banana正式上线后，已经刷爆了我的所有社交媒体，而它，现在也成了AI绘图领域，口喷改图的当之无愧的版本真神。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500190867\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1440536013400335\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"597\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6e826eb0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURogp9O1PzUhR5Jt2oNyzzCziakZjYmrVTHj032zYAXbMMnmOc0XSKwcI002zZicfePTba0kucF5OX9g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然我前几天写过一篇Nano Banana的</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&amp;mid=2647674193&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=584633fe8a001d6aee0b9476c3d6b84a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"人物一致性新王Nano Banana登基，AI图片编辑史诗级升级\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">人物一致性新王Nano Banana登基，AI图片编辑史诗级升级</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，但当时它还只能在lmarena上抽卡，不是很方便。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且我觉得，上次写的那篇，因为受制于Imarena的盲测属性，没法把Nano Banana的功力完全发挥出来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是现在，无论是推特公众号还是小红书上，都有太多颠覆的例子了，我自己也爽完了两天，说实话，只是改个背景改个服装，已经完全不够用了==</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以今天，再来加更一期，Nano Banana最新用法合集，让大家看看这玩意有多强。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">话不多说，直接开始。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">一. 制作手办</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最近最出圈的用法，没有之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这是提示词：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">create a 1/7 scale commercialized figure of thecharacter in the illustration, in a realistic styie and environment.Place the figure on a computer desk, using a circular transparent acrylic base without any text.On the computer screen, display the ZBrush modeling process of the figure.Next to the computer screen, place a BANDAl-style toy packaging box printedwith the original artwork.</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我先做了一个芙宁娜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500190830\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6351851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=05028057&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURogp9O1PzUhR5Jt2oNyzzCzVRPkM09rGsibx4C7qwUfqQPklkGRBlxwzibqzJ80qxNmibxNfefl9aZjA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后做了一个猫。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">NB真的很细，连脏脏的猫脚都还原了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500190831\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6759259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2272a297&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURogp9O1PzUhR5Jt2oNyzzCzibfgjzmvR5GHKbptoOIqXBDaDOm9icOo2R1QXzP83j9nzYh2aGIhFaSg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">兴致所至，我还做了一个老朋友。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500190807\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1024\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e0876c1d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURogp9O1PzUhR5Jt2oNyzzCzfk2uveMTxjTnA7yjZ7jEp23OWMMibCJPNkcjhgmclLS9vEibpUzGicmeg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">二. 玩cosplay</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">只需要给NB一张你的照片，和你想cos的角色的照片，提示词非常简单：让图一的人物cosplay图二的角色，服饰、妆容、道具和图二一致。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500190808\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7379629629629629\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1670\" data-height=\"1232\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0f3f0a14&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURogp9O1PzUhR5Jt2oNyzzCzud2kOIqHetV2ElRXn8dA7a3pvrbQZbSFj0WriafTT1XLzsgD4xIdIiag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后你就会得到——</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500190806\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.6\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"800\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f10d8758&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURogp9O1PzUhR5Jt2oNyzzCz5YhIuc4tA72SvunuUH5G38fMdsjHKvt9JuibmVb6JJT3Gv3rR042o5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然没有完全还原，枪长的不太一样，脖子上的项圈有些微的不同，裤子也不是及膝裤而是长裤。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但整体的效果，还是很对味的，而且服装道具啥的都还挺有质感的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">三. 换动作</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还是用上面cosplay的栗子。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">提示词：让图二的人物做出图一的动作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">NB的理解能力还是有点强的，即使只是给它画一堆火柴人，它也知道你是啥意思。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500190832\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.37037037037037035\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2e779508&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURogp9O1PzUhR5Jt2oNyzzCzaIwYrH6RYPdbSEsYYyia3z2aia96ytxdyQO18bMmoicfiaNdPzI8QlswWA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我还挺喜欢它在金克斯身边加的这几道线条的，感觉多了一些动漫感，有种次元壁打破的感觉。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500190811\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.36944444444444446\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"2226\" data-height=\"823\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6a4533c1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURogp9O1PzUhR5Jt2oNyzzCzkQZp7L9Wd0gUrNiaVgZlYSDuDfZ0UicXboGNicUJeTVvMSxzBMu14alGw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后孩子打累了，倒头就睡。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500190813\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.28888888888888886\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"2722\" data-height=\"787\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bea71b47&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURogp9O1PzUhR5Jt2oNyzzCzDjGL3IicIcTWQH4HHD2icEteGtRPLUL945NBzG19sHlgwXY3IfCMSq8g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">是一个对灵魂画手很友好的功能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">四. 产品内部结构图</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后是这个生成产品内部结构的方式，太酷了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">提示词在此：Ultra-detailed exploded view of a product, metallic parts and electronic components floating in mid-air, perfectly aligned, revealing inner structure, futuristic technology aesthetic, 8K resolution, soft cinematic lighting, highly realistic.</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500190812\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4351851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"2326\" data-height=\"1012\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4d20c3c2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURogp9O1PzUhR5Jt2oNyzzCzBaBxvxEqaNJO3mcUVAx3YyOibypvKgP2aUGz7PMwtJ67U5IWt7uPbsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500190810\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2611111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"2359\" data-height=\"617\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b780dace&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURogp9O1PzUhR5Jt2oNyzzCzoyxWf5TibVYuLDH3Db83Q4U33ic9s20ROOkXOYVHSyae2OfEPT1zicF3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">生成完图片之后，还可以用可灵的首尾帧，直接做个视频。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">创作之间的衔接非常丝滑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">五. 转线稿&amp;上色</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">受到这位大佬的启发，我也试了试转线稿和上色的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">提示词：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attribute